    </item>
    <item>
      <title>购物和 Z 世代成为 Pinterest 自 2020 年以来增长最快的群体</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pinterest-revenue-surges-on-popularity-of-shopping-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Pinterest Inc. 公布的第一季度销售额和用户增长超出了华尔街的预期，这得益于其进军购物领域和对 Z 世代用户的关注，该公司股价创下三年多以来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pinterest-revenue-surges-on-popularity-of-shopping-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:07:49 GMT</pubDate>
